-- Screenshots for Sega Games.
--
-- List was generated initially from blueMSX's segadb file, and then updated with a few more entries.
--
-- Each game name must exactly match two screenshot filenames, one with _a suffix and the other with _b suffix.
--
-- Screenshots were initially taken from https://thumbnails.libretro.com/, modified to fit Novo Player's screenshots size,
-- then a few more were added afterwards.
--
--	Jan 2026 Sam Elsharif - Version 1
--	Jun 2026 Sam Elsharif - Version 2
--
